title: Creature (disambiguation)
content:
Creature may refer to:

  • The scenery object found on top of the Dark Wizards' Tower
  • Creature Creation, the creation of hybrid monsters in the basement of the Tower of Life
    • Homunculus, a creature encountered during the Tower of Life quest that creates monsters for the player to kill in Creature Creation
  • Creature of Fenkenstrain, a members' quest
  • Cute creature, a monster spy featured in Tree Gnome Stronghold and The Eyes of Glouphrie quests
  • Hopeless Creature, a monster players have to kill during A Soul's Bane quest
  • Hunter creatures, monsters that can be caught using the Hunter skill
  • Light creature, found in the chasm near Juna
  • Monster, an attackable character or being that is not player-controlled
  • Races, inhabitants of RuneScape
  • Swamp creature, a monster encountered during the Temple Trekking activity
 This page is used to distinguish between articles with similar names.
If an internal link led you to this disambiguation page, you may wish to change the link to point directly to the intended article.
